## For Ubuntu 14.04 LTS
// Install Erlang/OTP 18

- Add `deb http://packages.erlang-solutions.com/ubuntu precise contrib` to apt
  source list
- Do `apt-get update`
- Do `apt-get install erlang`


// Install Elixir

- Do `apt-get install elixir`


// Install RabbitMQ
- Do `apt-get install erlang-nox
- Download RabbitMQ package from http://www.rabbitmq.com
- Install via dpkg `dpkg -i rabbitmq-server_3.5.4-1_all.deb`

